e register panel<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Login\\/Registration: Option to remove the email confirmation text on the register<\\/li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/ldx.training\\/course\\/using-design-upgrade-learndash\\/lesson\\/du-login-registration\\/\\\">See documentation \\u2192<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.12 - October 11, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Alerts: Option to set a smaller, more compact alert size<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Documentation links to each panel, explaining every option in more detail<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Course Content Lists: Bottom padding applied when using \\\"Container\\\" style<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Hiding the \\\"Back to...\\\" link works again (bug introduced in LearnDash 3.2.3)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Grid Item shadows were not being displayed in the default state<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Renamed \\\"Course Page\\\" to \\\"Infobar\\\" since it now also includes the infobar on group pages<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Infobar: Renamed \\\"Course Status\\\" options to \\\"Infobar\\\" for better alignment with official LearnDash terminology<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Slightly reduced font size in sidebar navigation<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Progress Bar: \\u201c% Complete\\u201d was off-center on mobile devices<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Lesson\\/Topic Timer now inherits text color<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweaks:<\\/strong> CSS updates for compatibility with LearnDash 3.2.3.3 (see below)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Header content action buttons spacing\\/layout<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Sidebar Navigation: Removed rotation on collapse arrow because LearnDash is now including it<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.11.1 - August 7, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Tweaked:<\\/strong> Updated a few styles for compatibility with Uncanny Groups version 3.7<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.11 - July 20, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Group Courses List: Disable expand\\/collapse<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Ribbon alignment can now be set to top left or top right<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweaked:<\\/strong> Groups: Updated styles for group courses lists<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweaked:<\\/strong> Course Grid: All grid styles properly apply to group grids (when using [ld_group_list] or the \\\"LearnDash Group List\\\" block)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Option to hide breadcrumbs in Focus Mode now hides breadcrumbs on quiz pages<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Video embed fullscreen bug in Safari when using our Focus Mode content animation feature<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.10 - April 29, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New Integration:<\\/strong> Tin Canny Reporting: 12 new design options for those using the Tin Canny LearnDash Reporting plugin (<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=pNJhe5f2J-Q\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">watch video<\\/a>).\\u00a0<em>Tin Canny LearnDash Reporting plugin sold separately by Uncanny Owl.<\\/em><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Tin Canny Reporting: \\\"Launch Content\\\" button now uses Primary Button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Profile: Hide \\\"Your Courses\\\" Header<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Uncanny Groups: Applied colors &amp; tweaked styles for the [uo_groups_manage_progress] output<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweaked:<\\/strong> Uncanny Groups: A few other small tweaks to Uncanny Groups styles<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.9.3 - April 4, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Quizzes: Proper correct\\/incorrect highlighting for fill in the blank questions (bug introduced in LearnDash 3.1.4 or 3.1.5)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.9.2 - March 26, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Focus Mode &amp; Course Navigation: Apply strikethrough to completed items<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Width adjustment on buttons within LearnDash alert messages<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Adjusted CSS to account for issues on some sites using the SG Optimizer plugin to combine CSS files<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.9.1 - March 7, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Tweaked a few styles for LearnDash 3.1.4<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: \\\"Back to Course\\\" and \\\"Back to Lesson\\\" links were not being hidden<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: \\\"Hide ALL Bottom Buttons\\\" was incorrectly hiding next\\/previous navigation in header<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.9 - Released February 21, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Integration:<\\/strong> Upgraded styles for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wisdmlabs.com\\/group-registration-for-learndash\\/\\\">WisdmLabs Group Registration plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Integration:<\\/strong> Upgraded styles for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.uncannyowl.com\\/downloads\\/uncanny-learndash-groups\\/\\\">Uncanny Groups plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Content animation option on page load<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Navigation: Removed background color on inner lesson &lt;div&gt; tag<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Progress Bar: Increased space between bar &amp; \\\"% Complete\\\"<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> RTL: Focus Mode sidebar close icon positioning<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> RTL: Focus Mode \\\"Mark Complete\\\" checkmark icon overlap<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Removed:<\\/strong> Transition styles on tooltips because they were conflicting with default LearnDash behavior<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Updated CSS animation names to avoid theme\\/plugin conflicts<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.8 - Released January 14, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> New profile layouts, background &amp; text colors<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Profile avatar: Custom size<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Profile avatar: Added option to inherit global border radius<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Profile: Hide \\\"Expand\\\" link on mobile when \\\"Hide Expand\\/Collapse\\\" option is selected<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid Video Previews: Border radius now works properly for top corners<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Grid Video Previews: Black background color added behind video embeds<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Font sizes &amp; weights of several elements within the [ld_profile] summary section<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.7 - Released January 8, 2020<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New Integration:<\\/strong> Upgraded styles for WisdmLabs Reviews, Ratings &amp; Feedback Plugin (<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/ldx.design\\/design-upgrade-wisdmlabs-ratings-reviews\\/\\\">learn more<\\/a>). <em>WisdmLabs plugin sold separately.<\\/em><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.6.3 - Released December 30, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Max-width for the login &amp; registration forms so they don\'t stretch all the way across larger screens<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Removed:<\\/strong> Styling on Focus Mode logo images that was causing some taller logos to expand beyond the header area<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Login\\/Register Buttons: Slightly reduced the opacity of the shadows on hover<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.6.2 - Released December 17, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> CSS compatibility for upcoming Widget Areas for LearnDash plugin<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.6.1 - Released November 25, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Class name (.ldx-grid-course-complete) is applied to completed courses in the course grid<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Quiz Results: Added spacing between paragraphs &amp; lists in the quiz response message displayed on the results page<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Hello Elementor: Improved styles for better compatibility with the Hello Elementor theme<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Single &amp; Multiple Choice Questions: When an answer is answered incorrectly, the correct answer is highlighted in green (bug introduced in LD 3.1 with a class name change)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Tooltip alignment<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Focus Mode edge-to-edge setting: Better spacing for comments &amp; quiz content<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.6 - Released November 20, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Updated styles for Focus Mode comments<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> 7 new options for Focus Mode comments, including backgrounds, borders &amp; avatar shape<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Quizzes: Matrix sorting questions spacing issues<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> Quizzes: Matrix sorting questions use a slightly different style when viewing correct\\/incorrect answers after a quiz<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.5 - Released September 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The Simple Course Timer idle timeout modal now uses standard &amp; primary button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The \\\"Reset Progress\\\" button now uses primary button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The [uo_dashboard] progress bar now uses progress bar styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The [uo_dashboard] now uses \\\"complete\\/correct\\\" color for checkmark icons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The [uo_dashboard] course action buttons (start|resume) now use primary button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The [uo_dashboard] toolbar action buttons (expand|collapse) now use standard button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Uncanny LearnDash Toolkit Pro: The [uo_courses] enhanced course grid now inherits styles from your \\\"Course Grid\\\" settings.<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Under the Hood:<\\/strong> \\\"Course Grid\\\" settings no longer require the LearnDash Course Grid add-on to be active. They will always appear in the Customizer.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.4 - Released August 25, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> 8 new customization options for the course status area shown to non-enrolled users (at the top of the course page)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Login\\/Registration: Customize the color of the close icon<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Focus Mode: Brand logo no longer gets squished on medium-sized (i.e. tablet) devices<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Change:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Focus Mode: Edge-to-Edge setting now only applies to lessons, topics &amp; quizzes (assignments &amp; essays will inherit LearnDash width setting)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Login\\/Registration: Adjusted z-index to fix bugs with other LearnDash elements, as well as headers built with Elementor (z-index is now set to\\u00a0100)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.3 - Released August 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> 14 new customization options for the login\\/registration popup<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Edge-to-Edge setting removes padding on mobile (&lt;640px)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Translation:<\\/strong> Added Arabic translation (kudos <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/qara.me\\/\\\">Mohammad<\\/a>)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.2 - Released July 5, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Alerts: Change border, background &amp; text color for all 3 types of LearnDash alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Alerts: Remove alert icons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Alerts: Set a border width for all alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Quiz buttons now properly inherit your button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Alert icon position on smaller screens<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.1 - Released Jun 26, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<p><strong>Ribbon colors are back!<\\/strong> Thank you for the feedback. Keep it coming.<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Course Grid: Ribbon background &amp; text colors for default, enrolled, free &amp; custom ribbons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> When disabling expand\\/collapse on course content lists, it was also being disabled on the Profile<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.0.1 - Released Jun 24, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<p>I\'ve heard your feedback and will be adding back the ability to customize course grid ribbon colors in the next release (~5-8 days).<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Legacy: Button styles were not being properly applied when using the \\\"Legacy\\\" template<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Add space for \\\"Download Certificate\\\" button icon, and other small tweaks to buttons within alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Alerts: Vertically center all icons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Small improvements to spacing of username in header<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Improved styles when \\\"Mark Complete\\\" button is disabled<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> More specific button style to avoid some theme conflicts with link colors<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.0 - Released Jun 22, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>IMPORTANT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0LearnDash\'s color settings must be disabled for our plugin\'s colors to take effect<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Now compatible with the LearnDash 3.0 Active Template<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> New style options for focus mode, tooltips, course content, profile &amp; more<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Tons of updated styles for quizzes (no customization; just improved styles)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Options are now saved globally. Styles remain in place even when you switch themes.<\\/li>\\n<li>Official videos &amp; explanations of all settings will be released soon<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.3 - Released Mar 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Buttons are now displayed at the very bottom of each grid item<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.2 - Released Mar 11, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Added a min-width of 45px to the number column in the course content table. This accounts for up to 999 items on most devices &amp; themes, without forcing the number to a new line.<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Inline &amp; full-width buttons both work again<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.1 - Released Feb 8, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Bug that was preventing administrators from accessing a user\'s \\\"Edit Profile\\\" page in the admin area<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7 - Released Jan 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Set a custom URL for\\u00a0the \\\"Edit Profile\\\" link when using the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Enrolled Course Points\\\" in the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Small spacing adjustment to the list count numbers in course content tables<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Adjusted alignment of quiz headings when quizzes are displayed in the [ld_profile]\\u00a0shortcode<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.3 - Released Dec 13, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Boss. Theme: We are now compatible with the Boss. theme, but you need to deactivate the \\\"Boss for LearnDash\\\" plugin.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.2 - Released Dec 11, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Twenty Nineteen: Updated a few styles for compatibility with the Twenty Nineteen theme<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Confirmed compatibility with WordPress 5.0, Gutenberg and the Classic Editor plugin<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.1 - Released Nov 2, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> .pot file so Customizer text can be properly translated<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Woffice: Tweaked a few styles for compatibility with the Woffice theme from Alkalab<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6 - Released Oct 31, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> OceanWP: Ensured compatibility with OceanWP\'s new LearnDash styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> More specific button style for \\\"back to lesson\\\" button<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Dev:<\\/strong> Bug fix: Prefix a function name to avoid potential conflicts<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.7 - Released Oct 16, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Customizer options now have proper text domain, making them ready for translation<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Columns weren\'t working properly with some page builders<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Some styles weren\'t being applied when Course Grid shortcode was used with page builders<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Fixed issue with Course Grid item border styles<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.6 - Released Oct 15, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Primary Button colors now applied to buttons when using the [learndash_payment_buttons] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Grid column styles updated to be compatible with Course Grid version 1.5.1<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Course category selector background color was not being applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.5 - Released Oct 14, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Course Content\\\" header text<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Edit Profile\\\" link when using the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Added space between Topic table &amp; \\\"Mark Complete\\\" button<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Course Grid ribbon styles were not being applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.4 - Released Sep 18, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Course Grid: CSS was updated for better compatibility with the Divi plugin<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> A few small CSS optimizations so the plugin uses less code<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.3 - Released Sep 13, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Some course grid styles are now more specific so they override default styles<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.2 - Released Sep 12, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Quiz timer bar now accepts striped settings (if selected for the progress bar)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> \\\"Sending\\\" quiz bar was flowing outside of the content area in some cases (depending on progress bar settings)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.1 - Released Sep 11, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Added a small change for course grid columns on some themes that also use Bootstrap (ex: Uncode)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Quiz time limit bar now uses the same height, background color &amp; border radius as defined for the progress bar<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Button Styles: \\\"Print Your Certificate\\\", as well as several other quiz-related buttons, now correctly inherit the button styles (\\\"Click Here to Continue\\\", \\\"Finish Quiz\\\", \\\"Restart Quiz\\\")<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5 - Released Sep 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> 24 new options for the LearnDash Course Grid add-on<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Better styles for the \\\"not available\\\" message when a lesson is scheduled for a later date<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Force \\\"Mark Complete\\\" buttons to have a hand pointer on hover<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Updated topic dots to use CSS background colors instead of images<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Removed:<\\/strong> Animation for \\\"sending quiz...\\\" progress bar. It was preventing the quiz bar from completely finishing in some implementations.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.4 - August 19, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Table border width &amp; color can now be customized<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Small, medium or large padding can be applied to each row<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Navigation Widget: Small, medium or large padding can be applied to each row<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Border radius wasn\'t being properly applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3.2 - August 17, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Link colors were not being applied to Expand\\/Collapse, \\\"back to course\\\" link in Course Nav Widget, and a few other spots<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Adjusted styles on progress bars and links within course content tables for better compatibility with Astra Pro<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Course content link styles now fully apply to Uncanny Toolkit\'s [uo_dashboard] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3.1 - August 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Quiz answer background colors were the same as text color, making them illegible<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> A few other CSS tweaks to make sure correct\\/incorrect colors were applied to quiz elements appropriately<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3 - August 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Completely revamped the quiz styles, including the quiz statistics popup<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Option to hide status checkmarks on Course Content lists<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Option to hide status checkmarks on Course Navigation Widget<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Status icons now appear in course content lists when using Divi LearnDash Kit<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> If expand\\/collapse was disabled for the course navigation widget, it was also applying to the course content lists<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.2.1 - August 2, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Now compatible with the Astra theme<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> A few small changes to button styles for better overall theme compatibility<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.2 - July 31, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Button Border Radius<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Navigation Widget: Move \\\"Return to Course\\\" link to the top<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Progress Bar: Display \'X out of Y steps completed\' above or below the bar<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Videos using Video Progression are now responsive by default<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Added back in button styles for the \\\"mark complete\\\" button. They were accidentally removed in the previous version. <em>(plus a few other button tweaks)<\\/em><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Lesson rows now accept the hover background color<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> A few CSS bugs with Uncanny Toolkit\'s [uo_dashboard] shortcode.<