.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>REQUISITOS&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Para este taller no necesitas tener conocimientos previos de cocina ni de preparación de conservas. Tampoco necesitarás complejos implementos ni materiales, lo fundamental es tener algunos frascos de vidrio con tapa, una olla grande, una tabla de picar, un cuchillo, una fuente y paños de cocina.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Al acceder a este taller te entregaremos en el material complementario, una lista con todos los materiales, ingredientes y recetas que necesitarás.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[bbp-single-forum id=373]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Taller de conservas','','inherit','closed','closed','','210-revision-v1','','','2021-04-17 15:12:44','2021-04-17 18:12:44','',210,'https://woocommerce-509196-1691061.cloudwaysapps.com/?p=437',0,'revision','',0),(439,1,'2021-04-17 15:20:47','2021-04-17 18:20:47','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[bbp-single-forum id=373]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Taller de conservas','','inherit','closed','closed','','210-revision-v1','','','2021-04-17 15:20:47','2021-04-17 18:20:47','',210,'https://woocommerce-509196-1691061.cloudwaysapps.com/?p=439',0,'revision','',0),(440,1,'2021-04-17 15:30:06','2021-04-17 18:30:06','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Foro del curso</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[bbp-single-forum id=373]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Taller de conservas','','inherit','closed','closed','','210-revision-v1','','','2021-04-17 15:30:06','2021-04-17 18:30:06','',210,'https://woocommerce-509196-1691061.cloudwaysapps.com/?p=440',0,'revision','',0),(441,1,'2021-04-17 15:31:21','2021-04-17 18:31:21','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Foro del curso</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[bbp-single-forum id=373]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Taller de conservas','','inherit','closed'